Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.75,0:02:24.27,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Vou simplismente continuar sobrevivendo neste mundo!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.27,0:02:29.34,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Ahh, a tristeza daquilo que perdemos está latejando de novo...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.53,OP BR,,0,0,0,,Um mundo de misérias!
